# Scene Settings
- Do not use default camera
- Use Canvas component
- Default pixel ratio: 1

# Performance Optimization
- Use BVH
- Utilize InstancedMesh
- Use compressed textures

# VRM Related
- Utilize BlendShapes
- Use SpringBone system
- Enable LookAt functionality

# Camera Settings
- FOV: 50
- Near: 0.1
- Far: 1000

# Control Settings
- Enable damping
- Damping Factor: 0.05
- Enable zoom
- Disable pan